<D>__{no, no, really... obviously you've got things you have to do. you've got to dismember the rest of his bloody torso. dig a makeshift shallow grave. cover the body with quick lime. really so much to do, so little time and i'm only in the way here, i'm just gonna go. good luck.}
<C>__{harriet}
<P>__{(referring to meat in hand)}
<D>__{oh, this! oh, no, this is what he stole. this isn't a piece of him or anything. this is icelandic shank.}
